            The objective of this study was to evaluate the capacity of spherical harmonics to detect and quantify DP in relation to conventional and extended anthropomorphic indexes. The distribution of the values of different indexes and coefficients for both groups (regular and with DP) is shown in Fig. 
            6
            .

